          <p>Mahalliy reseller bot orqali yangilash — bosqichma-bosqich:</p>

          <ol>
            <li><strong>@starsjoybot ni oching</strong> — Telegram'da <a href="https://telegram.me/starsjoybot" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@starsjoybot</a> ni topib, /start ni bosing</li>
