          </ol>

          <p>Hammasi to'g'ri bo'lsa, Premium aktiv. Agar 30 daqiqa ichida aktivlashmasa, <a href="https://telegram.me/starsjoysupport" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@starsjoysupport</a> ga yozing — operator tezda yordam beradi.</p>

